Type: Package
Package: InpatCGM
Title: Tools for Inpatient Continuous Glucose Monitoring (CGM) Data Analysis.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qi", "Yu", , "qi.yu2@emory.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Limin", "Peng", , "lpeng@emory.edu", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application and supporting tools for analyzing inpatient continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) data. Includes features for data cleaning, computing mean time in range (TIR), AGP metrics, stratified analysis, hypothesis testing, and report generation with dynamic plots and tables.
License: GPL (>= 3)
